em is also provided in the margins.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aTales, Medieval. 4aDISCOUNT-B. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Medieval.2bisacsh1 aGaudet, Minnette, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHieatt, Constance B., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press eBook-Package Archive 1933-1999z978311049094740uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144261657840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442616578423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442616578.jpg  a978-3-11-049094-7  University of Toronto Press eBook-Package Archive 1933-1999c1933d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK